As Janelle wrote to Dr. Math
On 09/21/2004 at 08:56:52 (Eastern Time),
>I think so.  Is the answer 29%.  52x = 1500/52 = 29%

Very good. To be more precise, you multiply 15 by 100 and divide by 
52, and get 28.846% as the answer. If you just need it rounded to 
the nearest percent, then your answer is just right.

Here is a page on working with percentages:

